The '''''Monstrous Compendium Annual Volume Three''''' is a 2{{nd}}-edition ''Advanced Dungeons & Dragons'' accessory

{{Quote|''Welcome to Year Three! Drawn from our best adventures! Drawn from our best adventures of 1995 - not to mention the award-winning [[dragon (magazine)|DRAGON]], [[dungeon magazine|DUNGEON]], and [[polyhedron magazine|POLYHEDRON]] Magazines - this annual also marks the return of many old classics and introduces some nifty new critters.
''More than 100 denizens of the land, sky, sea, and [[Outer Plane]]s are ready to sneak, storm, or wheedle their way out of these pages and into the nearest adventure. These creatures, many of them from the [[Forgotten Realms]], Birthright, [[Ravenloft]], Dark Sun, [[Al-Qadim]], and Greyhawk settings, are looking for new worlds to conquer.}}
